dear fernando,

i remember you and our lunch time chat very well. thanks again for your
interest in our work.

the 'treated' version of the uml metamodel can be found at:

   ftp://ftp.informatik.uni-bremen.de/local/db/papers/uml2004/

i say 'treated', because in many cases it was not clear to us how to
correct the bugs. 

if you are interested in the new version of the USE tool, you can find
our current developer version in the same directory. among other new
stuff, it includes a snapshot generator (see our uml2003 paper). we are
planning to put a release on the web very soon. any feedback is welcome!

best regards
martin

